data.alertmanager.yml:
global:
  resolve_timeout: 5m
receivers:
- name: default-receiver
  email_configs:
  - to: 'xxxxxxxxxxxx@126.com'
- name: alertsnitch
  webhook_configs:
    - url: http://alertsnitch:9567/webhook

route:
  group_interval: 5m # 5m
  group_wait: 30s # 30
  receiver: default-receiver
  repeat_interval: 24h # 
  group_by: [alertname]  # 
  routes:
  - receiver: default-receiver
    continue: true
  - receiver: alertsnitch
    continue: true
